ainham]] (2010)\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Frederick Burden|Burden]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[James Couchman|Couchman]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Paul Clark (politician)|Clark]]\n| colspan=\"8\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Rehman Chishti|Chishti]]\n|-\n|[[Gravesend (UK Parliament constituency)|Gravesend]] / [[Gravesham (UK Parliament constituency)|Gravesham]] (1983)\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[John Ovenden|Ovenden]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Timothy Brinton|Brinton]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Jacques Arnold|Arnold]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Chris Pond|Pond]]\n| colspan=\"9\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Adam Holloway|Holloway]]\n|-\n|[[Maidstone (UK Parliament constituency)|Maidstone]] / [[Maidstone and The Weald (UK Parliament constituency)|& The Weald]] (1997)\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[John Wells (20th-century British politician)|Wells]]\n| colspan=\"5\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Ann Widdecombe|Widdecombe]]\n| colspan=\"8\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Helen Grant (politician)|Grant]]\n|-\n|[[Rochester and Chatham (UK Parliament constituency)|Rochester & Chatham]] / [[Medway (UK Parliament constituency)|Medway]] (1983) / [[Rochester and Strood (UK Parliament constituency)|Rochester & Strood]] (2010)\n|bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Peggy Fenner|Fenner]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Robert Ernest Bean|Bean]]\n| colspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Peggy Fenner|Fenner]]\n| colspan=\"3\" bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Bob Marshall-Andrews|