rty (UK, 1931)|National Liberal]] (1931-68)|border=1px solid #aaaaaa}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Constituency\n!1918\n!1922\n!1923\n!1924\n!1929\n!''31''\n!1931\n!1935\n!1945\n!1950\n!1951\n!1955\n!1959\n!''60''\n!''63''\n!1964\n!1966\n!1970\n|-\n|[[Bedford (UK Parliament constituency)|Bedford]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Liberal/meta/color}}\" |[[Frederick George Kellaway|Kellaway]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"7\" |[[Sir Richard Wells, 1st Baronet|Wells]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Thomas Skeffington-Lodge|Skeffington-Lodge]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"7\" |[[Christopher Soames, Baron Soames|Soames]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Brian Parkyn|Parkyn]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Trevor Skeet|Skeet]]\n|-\n|[[Mid Bedfordshire (UK Parliament constituency)|Bedfordshire Mid]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Coalition Conservative/meta/color}}\" |[[Max Townley|Townley]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Frederick Caesar Linfield|Linfield]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[William Ward Warner|Warner]]\n| colspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"{{Liberal Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Milner Gray (politician)|Gray]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"7\" |[[Alan Lennox-Boyd, 1st Viscount Boyd of Merton|Lennox-Boyd]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"5\" |[[Stephen Hastings|Hastings]]\n|-\n|[[South Bedfordshire (UK Parliament constituency)|Bedfordshire South]]\n| colspan=\"9\" |\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Edward Warner Moeran|Moeran]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{National Liberal Party (UK, 1931)/meta/color}}\" colspan=\"5\" |[[Norman Cole (politician)|Cole]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Conservative Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Norman Cole (politician)|\u2192]]\n| bgcolor=\"{{Labour Party (UK)/meta/color}}\" |[[Gwilym Edffrwd Roberts|Roberts]]\n| bgcolor